  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-format document parsing (PDF, DOCX, PPTX, XLSX, HTML, images, audio)",
    "Advanced PDF understanding with layout analysis, table structure, and reading order",
    "Unified DoclingDocument representation format",
    "Multiple export formats (Markdown, HTML, JSON, WebVTT, DocTags)",
    "OCR support for scanned documents and images",
    "Visual Language Model (VLM) integration including GraniteDocling",
    "Automatic Speech Recognition (ASR) for audio/video files",
    "Information extraction and enrichment capabilities",
    "GPU acceleration support",
    "Native integrations with LangChain, LlamaIndex, Haystack, and Crew AI",
    "MCP server for agentic applications",
    "Plugin system for extensibility",
